Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:53.84,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}孤独を置いてきたみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:23:01.38,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今宵月も笑いかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:04.50,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}こっちを向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:09.60,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Oh, fly me to the star
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:32.78,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}気持ち伝えることできなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:43.96,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}色んな人生を浮かべ　演じてみるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:51.00,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あなたの気を惹きたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:55.94,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Oh, fly me to the star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:46.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我的双眼里永远只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:53.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}仿佛抛开了心底的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:23:01.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今夜的月色也绽开笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:04.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}请看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:09.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}带我遨游那美丽星海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.78,0:23:32.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}心里的情愫无法告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:43.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我选择扮演无数的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:51.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只为吸引你的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:55.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}带我遨游那美丽星海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:15.50,o-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ちょっと　待て
